overview: A Paolo O'Hara movie inspired by the 1986 Working Boys of the TVJ (Tito, Vic, and Joey). About the bums who need to strategize in life, the roles of the three are sloppy every time they strategize. All three are natural comics so they are very natural in their roles. The riot cast also includes Andrew Muhlach, Mikoy Morales, Bob Jbeili and Bayani Agbayani.
title: Working Boys 2: Choose Your Papa
